{"tid":1340421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位冷靜少少，民眾鬥民眾正中賊婆下懷","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T00:11:04.000Z","uid":65072,"like":14,"dislike":179,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"5c63483da4907c0e563661eec0175911bf0f5b56","tid":1340421,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"【轉載】一班AO的分享<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1333615/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1333615/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4。「有關方面」已安排為數千人的不明人士，代替警察應付勇武派的衝擊，</span><br />\n<br />\n我有睇到立場妹妹俾人打，蘋果記者俾人打<br />\n警察懶理，官商鄉黑，大家而家呢刻都好嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但呢個係一個局，一個賊婆預設的局<br />\n民眾鬥民眾，令我哋初心五大訴求失焦<br />\n而為報復而去光復元朗，只會造成街頭血鬥<br />\nCCTBB等黨媒等呢刻等咗好耐<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係失去咗道得高地，失去國際間的支持</span><br />\n<br />\n而家呢刻，睇到班五毛好努力煽動緊大家報仇，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請大家諗其他更高級方法報仇，同鄉黑唔好硬碰</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住我地初心，同埋真正敵人係邊個</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9aa6bcd1a873294ee8c96de51cca435645acf88","tid":1340421,"uid":21456,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:01:27.000Z","msg":"黑社會撚係民眾咩 屌佢老母"},{"pid":"e6b44e840bd4f9f92a565d40713f3d1d699b4c08","tid":1340421,"uid":21456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"黑社會撚係民眾咩 屌佢老母"},{"pid":"bdbb0a121dd075ab2f7045f597dd4bf9d2a1847f","tid":1340421,"uid":235515,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"拆完佢祠堂再拆中聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地大把時間同你玩"},{"pid":"2fe8e7f2c83d3983824486c92cd833c29a5c67f4","tid":1340421,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"果班「民眾」就係政權一部分"},{"pid":"fe339919571b3b4766da82d18090c673cb3442fc","tid":1340421,"uid":20916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":